title: WEDNESDAY - Cowboys Drama

description:
It looks like there's drama in Big D (0:06) as some Cowboys players express discontent with the coaches. Head coach Mike McCarthy (0:37) addressed the situation on Tuesday. It's Tua time in Miami (1:30) as Tua Tagovailoa is named the starter for the Dolphins. We have the latest on Christian McCaffrey (2:12) and Good Morning Football's Nate Burleson gives us a preview of what's to come on the show (2:42)
